Tolerates missing target or missing target.package instead of failing.
Normalizes both edge.spec and edge.rawSpec with npa.resolve(...),
only raises EOVERRIDE when they resolve to different actual paths.

Index: workspaces/arborist/lib/node.js
--- workspaces/arborist/lib/node.js.orig
+++ workspaces/arborist/lib/node.js
@@ -792,8 +792,11 @@ class Node {
 
